dc_description_s: This data represents addresses for Lincoln County, Wisconsin in 2025. [This feature class consists of Address Point information obtained predominantly by conducting field work using GPS technology and Orthophotography. This is a production level feature class where Address Points are edited and managed by Lincoln County Land Information Staff and then published to serve the needs of the public.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
